{"tid":1600834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日後再係咁相信唔會再有和理非出現，預左比人屌","createTime":"2019-09-28T18:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T19:28:26.000Z","uid":264091,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e888852cf1798e00f7871dab13dd8953f76e80f4","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"勇武歸勇武，勇武係有腦咁去勇<br />\n<br />\n屯門個次再次講番個事實出泥<br />\n係有個手足拎住把唔知邊度泥既氣槍射班狗<br />\n班黑警就有機會入你舉旗話你挑釁，不過的確係我地挑釁在先<br />\n之後屯門被逼散場<br />\n<br />\n今日和理非集會<br />\n可以引用天埼語錄「不要被憤怒蓋過理智」<br />\n噴你一下胡椒噴霧，就全部人落曬去圍政總<br />\n之後集會又要提早結束<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬，佢講明成廿萬人出左泥，個幾鐘集會就要走，又要冒住被狗咬既風險，係我都唔出，大西北既又遠，番去唔容易架我想講。<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以搵一次，等成個集會完左先圍先去打，真既，可唔可以溝通好啲，我都係上前面發開夢，唔好同我講你實未落過前線睇，我就係睇完之後覺得呢件事要改，講完。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76f1ce4e5da77cc52388c7289857f83907b89cb","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"P牌自推<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"cec0bf014d615d30709911d582fc9a76e9ddba97","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:22:22.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"51cebca01f65a774191a0f208f9333737e2cdd7a","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"181834cdea305b19a9b90c6559059733438ef104","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:22:47.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"995cdc4a3327c0ec6e834d01297bd46a2e0545bf","tid":1600834,"uid":264091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"22ecefda41c372220eea32cd2099a1454525489a","tid":1600834,"uid":224479,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T18:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99187a5cd10af1aab56d16aee1313fff00a76796","tid":